Interface Branch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Aclf3WBranch, AclfBranch, Acsc3WBranch, AcscBranch, BaseHvdcLine2TVSC<TBus>, BaseOpfBranch, Branch3W, DclfOpfBranch, DistBranch, DStab3WBranch, DStabBranch, Dynamic3PBranch, HvdcLine2T, HvdcLine2TCCC, HvdcLine2TVSC, HvdcLine2TVSCDyn, HvdcLine2TVSCDynPlus, OpfBranch, Steady3PBranch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Aclf3WBranchImpl, AclfBranchImpl, Acsc3WBranchImpl, AcscBranchImpl, BaseHvdcLine2TVSCImpl, BaseOpfBranchImpl, Branch3WImpl, BranchImpl, DclfOpfBranchImpl, DistBranchImpl, DStab3WBranchImpl, DStabBranchImpl, Dynamic3PBranchImpl, HvdcLine2TCCCImpl, HvdcLine2TImpl, HvdcLine2TVSCDynImpl, HvdcLine2TVSCImpl, OpfBranchImpl, Steady3PBranchImpl

    public interface Branch
extends ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel
    A representation of the model object 'Branch'. Branch class for representing a 2-terminal branch concept for power system simulation. The branch has two terminals, connecting to two buses.

    The following features are supported:

    • Circuit Number
    • Child Branch
    • From Side Metered
    • Network
    • To Bus
    • From Bus
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getBranch()
